sequenceDiagram
participant User 
participant Browser
participant SPA
participant Server
participant Database

User->>SPA: Write a new note in the text field
User->>SPA: Click "Save"
SPA->>Server: Send POST request with new note data (JSON)
Server->>Database: Save new note to the database
Database-->>Server: Confirm note saved
Server-->>SPA: Respond with success message and updated notes list (JSON)
SPA-->>Browser: Update the user interface with the new note
Browser-->>User: Display updated list of notes
